statements: SELECT * FROM trade_order_executions;
SELECT symbol, executed_price FROM trade_order_executions ORDER BY execution_timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM trade_order_executions WHERE order_status = 'OPEN' ORDER BY executed_price DESC;
SELECT symbol, executed_volume FROM trade_order_executions WHERE executed_volume >= 1000;
SELECT trade_id, symbol, execution_timestamp FROM trade_order_executions WHERE execution_timestamp >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY execution_timestamp ASC;
SELECT * FROM trade_order_executions WHERE executed_price > 100 AND executed_volume >= 50 ORDER BY execution_timestamp DESC
SELECT symbol, executed_price FROM trade_order_executions WHERE order_status = 'FILLED' ORDER BY trade_id ASC
SELECT trade_id, symbol, executed_volume FROM trade_order_executions WHERE executed_price BETWEEN 50 AND 100 ORDER BY trade_id DESC
SELECT * FROM trade_order_executions WHERE symbol LIKE 'AAPL%' AND order_status IN ('OPEN', 'PENDING')
SELECT trade_id, execution_timestamp FROM trade_order_executions WHERE executed_volume < 20 ORDER BY execution_timestamp ASC
SELECT * FROM TradeExecutions WHERE id = 1;
SELECT execution_price, executed_quantity FROM TradeExecutions WHERE trade_id = 100 ORDER BY execution_price DESC;

SELECT symbol, closing_price FROM historical_data WHERE symbol = 'AAPL' AND closing_price > 200 ORDER BY timestamp ASC;

SELECT trade_symbol, quantity FROM TradeHistory WHERE price > 100;
